de.lambeck.pned.models.gui

Interface IUndoableModel

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    IGuiModel
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    GuiModel, UndoRedoElementBuffer

    interface IUndoableModel
    Interface for an IGuiModel with Undo/Redo capabilities

    Note: Visibility is limited to this package to prevent external classes from interfering with Undo/Redo operations because the IGuiModelController has to write elements back into the IGuiModel without further plausibility checks.
    Author:
    Thomas Lambeck, 4128320
